  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Requires the department of veterans' services to provide legal and/or technical support to veterans who want to change their discharged status to honorable because such person was dishonorably or administratively discharged from the armed services due to sexual orientation."
    }
